snippet.title: Age of Empires IV - Interview with Bert Beeckman - Gamescom 2022 Xbox Booth
snippet.description:
Studio Head of Forgotten Empires, Bert Beeckman, is back to share details on the new FREE civilizations, Ottomans and Malians, and some of their special units in Age of Empires IV.

Stay connected with Age of Empires!
